### Test Baileys WhatsApp Gateway API

### 1. Check API Status
GET http://localhost:3000/

### 2. Create Session
POST http://localhost:3000/api/session/create
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-KEY: baileys-gateway-secret-key-2024

{
  "sessionId": "test-session"
}

### 3. Get Session Status (JSON)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/session/test-session/status
X-API-KEY: baileys-gateway-secret-key-2024

### 4. View QR Code in Browser
# Open in browser: http://localhost:3000/qr/test-session

### 5. Send Text Message (after connected)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/message/text
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-KEY: baileys-gateway-secret-key-2024

{
  "sessionId": "test-session",
  "to": "6281234567890",
  "message": "Hello from API!"
}

### 6. Get All Sessions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/sessions
X-API-KEY: baileys-gateway-secret-key-2024

### 7. Delete Session
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/session/test-session
X-API-KEY: baileys-gateway-secret-key-2024
